name: Torrie Lewis
summary: Australian sprint prodigy Torrie Lewis has sent shockwaves through the athletics world, stunning reigning world 100-meter champion Sha'Carri Richardson in a "Holy crap" moment at the Xiamen Diamond League meet in China.
